Transatlantic Holdings Sues Validus Over Acquisition Proposal

-- B y   P h i l   M i l f o r d
-- 
2011-07-28T13:41:48Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-28/transatlantic-sues-validus-to-stop-statements-in-reinsurer-takeover-fight.html
Transatlantic Holdings Inc. (TRH) , a
global reinsurance firm, sued  Validus Holdings Ltd. (VR)  in
federal court in Delaware contending the rival company is trying
to mislead Transatlantic stockholders into tendering their
shares in violation of  securities law , according to court records.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Phil Milford in Wilmington, Delaware at 
 pmilford@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
